# Liquid root .gitignore
#
# Per-tree .gitignore files (e.g. core/.gitignore, app/.gitignore) cover
# patterns specific to that subtree. This file covers patterns that
# apply repo-wide.

# ─── Editor / IDE ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.idea/
.vscode/
*.swp
*.swo
*~
.DS_Store

# ─── OS ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
Thumbs.db
ehthumbs.db
Desktop.ini

# ─── Local environment / secrets (CLAUDE.md deny rules also block reads) ─
.env
.env.*
!.env.example
secrets/
*.pem
*.key
*.keystore
*.jks
*.p12
**/google-services.json
**/GoogleService-Info.plist

# ─── Rust ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Build artifacts (also covered by core/.gitignore for the workspace).
**/target/
**/*.rs.bk
Cargo.lock.bak

# Crash dumps from Rust panics
**/crash.log

# ─── Flutter / Dart ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Generated build output
**/build/
.dart_tool/
.flutter-plugins
.flutter-plugins-dependencies
.packages
.pub-cache/
.pub/

# Flutter IDE files
**/.flutter-plugins
**/ios/Flutter/Flutter.framework
**/ios/Flutter/Flutter.podspec
**/macos/Flutter/ephemeral
**/android/.gradle/
**/android/local.properties
**/android/captures/

# flutter_rust_bridge generated files (committed under app/lib/bridge/)
# are intentionally NOT ignored.

# ─── Lockfile policy ────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Cargo.lock IS tracked (workspace level) — we ship reproducible builds.
# pubspec.lock IS tracked once Flutter packages exist.

# ─── AI / agent artifacts ───────────────────────────────────────────────
# .claude/ is the repo-local AI agent config — it IS tracked.
# .ai/ holds run-time agent artefacts (raw logs, diffs, screenshots) —
# these are session-local and should not be committed. The single
# tracked file is .ai/artifacts/README.md (documents the convention);
# .ai/artifacts/.gitignore handles the per-subtree exceptions.
.ai/*
!.ai/artifacts/

# Per-developer Claude Code settings overlay — local only.
.claude/settings.local.json

# ─── Coverage / profiling ───────────────────────────────────────────────
*.profraw
*.profdata
coverage/
lcov.info

# ─── Misc ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Temporary files written by editors or test fixtures
/tmp/
*.bak
*.tmp
*.orig
*.rej
